{
  "texts": [
    "By leveraging contextawareness, IoT applications can provide personalized and proactive services, optimizing resource usage and improving overall efficiency [17].",
    "In this paper, we provide a comprehensive overview of the current research on CA IoT systems.",
    "We review the state-of-the-art techniques and technologies for capturing and processing contextual information.",
    "In the upcoming sections we focus on the key research challenges we face during the development of context aware-IoT Systems.",
    "Our focus remains on the domains scalability, interoperability, security and privacy."
  ]
}